, \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Serb had to withdraw from this year's French Open due to an injury.\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3768, \"end\": 3772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9946439965139039, \"rank\": 0.004872846326828758, \"text\": \"Serb\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No matter how you look at it, Sunday's men's singles final between Alcaraz and Djokovic is massive.\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3904, \"end\": 3911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.700841125709574e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 3916, \"end\": 3924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999708962, \"rank\": 2.894488355443567e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair are tied head-to-head with three wins each -\\u00a0their last meeting being just a month ago at theWimbledonfinal, which Alcaraz won.\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 4073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4061, \"end\": 4068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.700841125709574e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The winner on Sunday will make history as the youngest (Alcaraz) or oldest (Djokovic) to win gold in the Olympics men's singles tournament.\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4130, \"end\": 4137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.700841125709574e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are the results of the duo's six matches against each other:  2024 Wimbledon - Final: Alcaraz wins 6-2 6-2 7-6(4)2023 ATP Finals - Semi-final: Djokovic wins 6-3 6-22023 Cincinnati Masters - Final: Djokovic wins 5-7 7-6(7) 7-6(4)2023 Wimbledon - Final: Alcaraz wins 1-6 7-6(6) 6-1 3-6 6-42023 Roland-Garros - Semi-final: Djokovic wins 6-3 5-7 6-1 6-12022 Madrid Masters - Semi-final: Alcaraz wins 6-7(5) 7-5 7-6(5)  We want to hear it.\", \"from\": 4214, \"to\": 4653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4305, \"end\": 4312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.700841125709574e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 4471, \"end\": 4478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.700841125709574e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 4602, \"end\": 4609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.700841125709574e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Send us a tip using our anonymous form.\", \"from\": 4654, \"to\": 4693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rolling Stone is a part of Penske Media Corpora